4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%A7n-Ch%C3%A2u-ki%E1%BA%BFn-s%E1%BA%AFc-m%E1%BB%A5c-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-tam-C%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BB%A5-t%C6%B0-ngh%E1%BB%8B-lang-T%E1%BA%A5t-t%E1%BB%A9-Di%E1%BB%87u-tr%E1%BB%AB-gi%C3%A1m-s%C3%A1t-d%E1%BB%AF-nh%E1%BB%8B-t%E1%BB%AD-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BB%91-vi%E1%BB%85n-h%E1%BB%89/poem-MckcrDzR5IMVz8q99e9tfA">Tần Châu kiến sắc mục Tiết tam Cứ thụ tư nghị lang, Tất tứ Diệu trừ giám sát, dữ nhị tử hữu cố viễn, hỉ thiên quan kiêm thuật tác cư, hoàn tam thập vận - 秦州見敕目薛三璩授司議郎畢四曜除監察與二子有故遠喜遷官兼述 索居凡三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/Thu%E1%BB%B7-long-ng%C3%A2m-Vi-H%C3%A0n-Nam-Gi%E1%BA%A3n-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-th%E1%BB%8D-Gi%C3%A1p-Th%C3%ACn-tu%E1%BA%BF/poem-xHy7QQigZcNKYCKj2TW_jA">Thuỷ long ngâm - Vi Hàn Nam Giản thượng thư thọ Giáp Thìn tuế - 水龍吟－為韓南澗尚書壽甲辰歲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/V%C4%83n-ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%E1%BA%A1o-ho%C3%A1/poem-boytAa5rhaC091PfFfOr4A">Văn chương tạo hoá - 文章造化</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Chu-V%C4%83n-An/poem-w0GgquYtfAVcoL3oiMfAsQ">Vịnh Chu Văn An - 詠朱文安</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
